        <div class="tutorialSubheading">
            <h2>The Definition of Computer Science and Coding</h2>
        </div>
        <p>
            <li>Computer science is the study of computers and computing concepts.</li>
            <li>Coding, often confused as being the same thing as computer science, is
            the instructions in a computer program.</li>
        </p>
        <div class="tutorialSubheading">
            <h2>Languages</h2>
        </div>
        <p>
            <li>A programming language is a set of commands, instructions,
            and other syntax used to instruct a computer to perform
                specific tasks.</li>
            <li>Examples: Java, Javascript, Python, and Swift.</li>
            <li>This website was built using Javascript, HTML, and CSS. Javascript programs
            the behavior of the webpage and is a more sophisticated and difficult
            language than HTML and CSS, which contain standard words, rather than
